<p>In conclusion, this analysis provides a wider perspective on Indian science. Above table, Fig <a href="#fig6">6</a> and <a href="#fig7">7</a> suggest that publication trends of Indian researchers were similar to that of US and China. However, properly curated data should be able to provide us with a more clear picture.</p>

